        <abstract>
            <p>Sorry he cannot remember where S. Filippe [San Felipe?] is.</p> 
<p>Doubts that bones of ox, sheep, and horse could have been deposited in <hi rend="italic">guano</hi> [on coast of Chile], but they would be worth examination.</p>  
<p>[Tipped in copy of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> (1866) with CHM’s bookplate.]</p> 
        </abstract>
